txt.en: 'You are not like all the other little ones.  You are much more.  You saved us.  Thank you for saving the forest.  We shall stand guard now and protect the forest.'
'Who dares destroy our forest? We cannot have these Orcs scurrying about ruining our lands.  All little ones must be crushed.'
'Trolls made of fire?  Come!  These bigger ones are the worst of all.'
